"For our second episode of Edge & Main, Future of Good’s podcast on the trends, tensions, and transformations of today that will define the world of tomorrow, we sat down with Indy Johar, co-founder of Dark Matter Labs.

Dark Matter Labs designs institutional infrastructure for a distributed and collaborative future, working with partners, clients, and collaborators across the world to research and develop new support frameworks for collaborative system change."

